    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into thin slices (reserve for garnish!) and juice the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon </strong>into a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>honey</strong>, a sprinkle of your <strong>cornflour</strong>,<strong> half </strong>of your <strong>soy sauce </strong>(save the rest for later!) and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>to the bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lemon sauce</strong></p>",
