    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> lengthways into 2 strips per person, then cut each strip in half</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cornflour</strong> to a bowl along with 1 tsp [<span class=\"text-purple\">1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, your <strong>five-spice mix </strong>and a generous grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and mix it all together</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken strips</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix up until all the chicken is coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
