      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy chicken </strong>and<strong> roasted Tenderstem broccoli </strong>over the <strong>chilli rice</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>lemon sauce</strong> over the chicken and garnish with the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>lemon slices</strong> and<strong> toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
